## Disclaimer

This project is provided for educational and demonstration purposes. While
it follows best practices and is production-ready, users should review and
test the code thoroughly before using it in production environments.

The mock data and API simulations are for demonstration purposes only and
should be replaced with real data sources in production applications.

## Support

This project is maintained as an open-source educational resource. While
we welcome contributions and feedback, please note that this is not a
commercial product with guaranteed support.

For questions, issues, or contributions, please use the GitHub repository's
issue tracker and pull request system.

